15#ifndef ISC_FORMATCHECK_H
16#define ISC_FORMATCHECK_H 1
17
18/*! \file isc/formatcheck.h */
19
20/*%
21 * ISC_FORMAT_PRINTF().
22 *
23 * \li fmt is the location of the format string parameter.
24 * \li args is the location of the first argument (or 0 for no argument checking).
25 *
26 * Note:
27 * \li The first parameter is 1, not 0.
28 */
29#ifdef __GNUC__
30#define ISC_FORMAT_PRINTF(fmt, args) __attribute__((__format__(__printf__, fmt, args)))
31#else
32#define ISC_FORMAT_PRINTF(fmt, args)
33#endif
34
35#endif /* ISC_FORMATCHECK_H */
